Comment: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:01.71,Ristorante,,0000,0000,0000,,A Husband and Wife
Comment: 0,0:20:52.16,0:21:00.80,Ristorante,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,A Special Day
Comment: 0,0:22:39.43,0:22:42.49,Ristorante,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like you should... watch next time, huh?

Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:11.33,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,After a fight, we go out for a good dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:15.50,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,We've been doing so since before we got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:21.21,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,This is horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.21,0:00:23.37,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,People said the food was good, so my hopes were high,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:25.64,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,but not a single dish was anything special.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.64,0:00:28.05,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Teo, people can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.05,0:00:31.33,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,You think? I thought it was quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.33,0:00:33.54,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better rethink your definition of good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:35.87,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise I won't let you prep the ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.20,0:00:38.91,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,It does look like the chef has changed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:42.14,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping you could learn a thing or two, Nicoletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:45.73,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well. 'Twas a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.43,0:00:59.90,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't as bad as they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.90,0:01:02.40,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, the quality dropped a little bit, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.76,0:01:06.92,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't your first time there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.51,0:01:13.54,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. I'm sure one of your midnight liaisons began there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.54,0:01:16.68,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't we going there to celebrate making up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.68,0:01:17.51,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.79,0:01:21.43,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,But you're not out of the doghouse yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.12,0:01:26.39,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Gelato!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.39,0:01:27.62,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to freeze?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:03:02.77,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever find yourself in Rome, go look for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:08.99,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,The mysterious ristorante full of bespectacled gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.82,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,This wine is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:19.53,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll take another glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:21.81,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, as soon as you finish that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:23.26,Ristorante,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:27.76,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I wish my husband would do these things for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:31.02,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,An expensive wine is nice from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:33.32,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Can you recommend me something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:35.28,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for a recommendation...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:36.45,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Gigi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:39.41,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,What do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:42.04,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,He's a veteran sommelier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:42.90,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:44.91,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,And your budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:47.53,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:49.81,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't give her a Tuscan red.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:53.50,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps a Piemonte? The recent whites have been selling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:56.59,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the Sardinians go well with seafood, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:58.43,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,The whites from Le Marche go well with seafood pasta dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.83,0:03:58.43,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lucia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:04:00.15,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Gianna, you're here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:04.16,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,You know, yesterday I saw your husband with some woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:08.17,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Again? Once a playboy, always a playboy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:10.69,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,He's always talking up the women at the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.69,0:04:13.02,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm OK with it as long he doesn't get serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:19.11,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but it wasn't the first time I've seen him with a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:19.71,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:23.10,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,And this was the same woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:27.62,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's freezing out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:31.69,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, something smells great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:33.17,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I rented us a DVD.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:39.63,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a good movie the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:42.09,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? What was it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:46.99,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,About a husband who sneaks off to cheat on his wife and what she does afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.13,0:04:51.93,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm not talking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:54.79,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you're just extra nice to girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:57.04,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you're cheating on me or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:05:00.16,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,So, there was this scene in the film.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:02.74,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,The husband decides to come home for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:07.37,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,The wife is hard at work at dinner. Suddenly she breaks a bottle of wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:13.12,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,The shards of glass end up in the pasta, and the husband eats them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:15.09,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't do it on purpose, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:17.79,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the husband storms off, in a fit of rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:22.38,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,That scene really left a deep impression in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:24.21,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,You don't say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:30.81,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear. I broke the wine bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.09,0:05:36.83,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. The shards didn't get in the pasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.88,0:05:39.52,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,We have another bottle, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:40.82,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:46.87,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. He has a mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:51.06,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you been married?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:54.20,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Two years. And we dated for two years before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:57.90,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,He's been obsessed with women since back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:00.01,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't mean that he was a serial dater.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:05.03,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,He works as a salesman and picks up lots of women who come to his store.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:08.01,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,But back then, he was just fooling around, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:12.57,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But this last discretion was the final straw.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:17.02,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,My friend told me to see a specialist and sent me to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:20.57,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,First, you'd divvy up your assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.57,0:06:23.19,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Then, a three-year legal separation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:26.90,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,After that, you can finally request a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.23,0:06:28.15,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:31.66,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Getting divorced takes a lot of time and energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:34.44,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,so please make sure you're properly prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:40.54,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Furio's giving cooking lessons?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:45.02,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He said he runs them on his days off at the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.02,0:06:46.77,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Well, do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:49.09,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Say you will and I'll give you extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:50.56,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,It's just some unsold things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:51.18,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:52.87,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:56.65,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get really good at cooking and Teo will see me in a new light!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:07:01.20,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,OK, today's lesson will be beef stew with polenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:03.16,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:05.07,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:12.87,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Enjoying your first day?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:15.20,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,You bet! It's a lot of fun and I'm learning a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.00,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:19.08,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Teach me lots, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:20.72,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:23.09,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Just who do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:24.85,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Furio belongs to all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:28.51,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What? U-Uh... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:37.29,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,That was tough in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:40.26,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the women are big fans of Furio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.26,0:07:43.48,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it. And you're not, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:46.04,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I wouldn't really call myself a fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:50.53,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,You're the new apprentice at the ristorante, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:52.78,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about you from Vito.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:54.36,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:56.87,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Marina, Vito's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:58.37,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:02.00,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,He's so used to haute cuisine,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:05.00,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm coming here to get better at cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:06.14,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:07.75,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:09.31,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:15.08,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Man, was that a shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:19.02,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,She's no older than I am - Vito's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:23.54,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,But still, she's not uncomfortable?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:24.48,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:26.59,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.56,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:32.33,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:35.11,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't sit right with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:37.55,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Vito's really popular with the ladies,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:39.99,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,and he's so much older than her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:46.70,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the only ones who know what goes on between a married couple is the husband and wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:52.45,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,If it bothers you, why don't you ask Vito himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:00.50,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I'm honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:03.12,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,To think you'd worry about us so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:05.90,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave it to your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:10.72,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,For I worship all the women of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:12.23,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I beg your pardon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:13.29,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:17.02,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can't help it if you're concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:21.42,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, I was the one who asked {\i1}her{\i0} out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:22.58,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:23.70,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:27.66,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,It was a chance encounter of destiny, in the gym I used to go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:30.68,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,'Twas love at first sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:33.06,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I was after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.06,0:09:37.69,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Then one day, there was a chance encounter at a karate dojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:42.44,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,And then, thanks to a puzzle magazine I had in a broken elevator,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:45.71,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to pop the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:46.69,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,There you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:50.19,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,How much of that am I supposed to believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.68,0:09:53.07,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,That's up to you, Nicoletta, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.13,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,God!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:58.20,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Another glass, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:03.40,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,How about you tell her how you and Marina really got to know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:07.99,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,No, I cannot betray my wife's privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.99,0:10:11.80,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,A gentleman must harbor a secret or two, don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:17.80,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, the day you requested is coming soon, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:20.84,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:29.05,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,So I need to prepare myself for the divorce, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:41.63,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,He's all over the place, but it's not like I can't love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:44.62,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I do love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:50.13,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,He just pisses me off. He really uses me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:56.88,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I should fool around, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.75,0:11:01.01,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Buonasera.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:02.57,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Buonasera.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.42,0:11:06.54,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,We've got customers at table two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:08.65,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Antipasto, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:09.60,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,On it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:13.05,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Put a little extra salt in the second course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:17.03,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall, her sister prefers a little stronger flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:18.61,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:20.11,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:24.62,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, Vito's sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:26.68,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Marina's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:29.91,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,She's visiting Marina while coming to see her folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:31.12,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Her husband is here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.12,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:38.09,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, we've got a dish made with a yogurt marinade and tomato sauce...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:43.94,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Say, that's Marina's sister and her husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.94,0:11:45.76,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,The husband, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:48.46,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he's from another country.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:51.91,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,They spend most of their time there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:54.02,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:58.90,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,The three of them used to live here, in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:11:59.82,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:06.83,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,But well, there's a long story, but eventually she stayed behind, alone, here in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:11.82,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,When I first met her, Marina was still rough around the edges.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:18.09,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,But, ever since her and Vito got married, she's had a smile on her face, like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:26.69,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you tomorrow. Ciao.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.69,0:12:27.72,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Ciao.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.92,0:12:35.47,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Should they be leaving Marina and them here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:38.69,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. The wife will catch up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:44.70,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you for before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:48.45,Ristorante,FV+MV,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:52.75,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.44,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:03.57,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't get into my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:06.61,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot the key and Lucia's not in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:09.81,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,So you got lonely and came here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:11.51,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Did Lucia stop by?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:14.68,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,She sure did, and she left with Gigi just a few minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:18.89,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Kinda like somebody we know who leaves his wife to go fool around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.89,0:13:20.23,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Gigi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:25.39,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Gigi, yeah... He's been a good man since the age of twenty-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:27.87,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,He's really tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:31.41,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,He might even be taller than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:35.00,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Plus he's a master sommelier and a gifted conversationalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:37.25,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,There's not a woman who'd turn him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:44.51,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,This is to pay you back for the advice you gave me. OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.73,0:13:48.01,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Are you always this quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:53.79,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,She got sick and tired of you cheating on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:57.36,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,So why not go home with that blonde beauty?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:14:00.44,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Or whatever works for him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:02.48,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,You think you're so smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:03.54,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:09.03,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,If I had to wager a guess, it's because she was frustrated, and just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:12.29,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a glass on the house for being dumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:17.98,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Your wife is incredibly beautiful. Treat her well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:18.75,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:22.13,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better listen to what your senior tells you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:26.41,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you have a lot in common when it comes to women.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:29.98,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Women just can't resist wanting to accompany me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:31.48,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:34.14,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,They just decide they want to join me for dinner and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:38.64,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed. Which is why I never considered getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:42.33,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I never wanted to hurt any one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:46.92,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,The girls knew what kind of guy I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:49.90,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,so only the ones looking for a good time approached me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:54.45,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,When those women weren't around, I was completely alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:58.37,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,But now, I've met my wife, whom I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:02.28,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, I get to thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.87,0:15:07.44,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,What would the two of us be doing, had we never met?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:13.43,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost positive I'd be spending my days all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:17.81,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,If what I'm describing would make you feel lonely,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:22.13,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,you'd better stop doing what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.99,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,And if you want to know about divorce, here's your guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:28.74,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,No better person to tell you about it than a divorcee.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:32.19,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, err... Umm... Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:36.99,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to hear Lucia say she's leaving you, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:47.55,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,There's something you need to keep in mind if you want a long, healthy marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:51.13,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Think hard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:01.93,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't come home again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:15.99,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I can't survive alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:22.15,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,But, I don't want to sit here all day waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:24.42,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,for my wife to come home from a date either!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:26.24,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,This is Friday night!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:37.85,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving again, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:42.48,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,"Again"? You've been out partying yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:45.84,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm allowed to go shopping with friends, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:47.86,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,It just ran a little late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:50.23,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Sure you weren't out with some guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:51.60,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,A guy named Gigi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:52.70,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Gigi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:55.69,Ristorante,,0000,0000,0000,,We had dinner the other night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:56.57,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,So you admit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.13,0:16:59.63,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,He's an older man and cute when he ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:03.08,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,He's older than my father, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.47,0:17:04.91,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:08.50,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,How about you? Which hot little thing are you going out with today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:11.65,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting for you to come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:13.59,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Dressed to go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:18.59,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Were you thinking about making things right with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:34.65,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, I was thinking about what I need to do in order to have a long, healthy marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:42.02,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I've been pondering the same thing, these last few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:44.69,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Did you figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:47.35,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:55.30,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,But you need to stop having flings with random women.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:58.90,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first step.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:01.76,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What did you come up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:05.29,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:07.77,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.59,0:18:13.37,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I made a reservation for dinner tonight, thinking we'd make up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:16.73,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting for you to come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:20.27,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me, Lucia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.36,0:18:26.33,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:28.91,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:33.37,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, the landlord called me. I wonder what it's about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:34.73,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:35.63,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Get changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:43.26,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,The one across the street... I've never set foot in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:47.31,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,but I think I heard it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:49.89,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,A table!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.53,0:18:51.90,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Buonasera.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:57.04,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I can ready a table for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:18:59.61,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,A couple just settled their tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:07.25,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Our top-notch sommelier, Gigi, will bring you an exquisite wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:13.93,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I believe he's already acquainted with your wife's tastes, so he can get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:19.20,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}are{\i0} coming with your wife tonight, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:25.31,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,This is a make-up dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:30.02,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Please give us the best food and wine you can, for her sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:33.02,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:40.93,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,He was totally silent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:42.86,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,He never says a word!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:45.70,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,That sommelier over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:46.20,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:48.41,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,But he sure picks a good wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:53.16,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Table five seems incredibly satisfied with dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:54.57,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's time for the dolce.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:55.33,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,On it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:05.89,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? You two are oddly getting along all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:07.29,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:10.78,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,No one charms the ladies like Vito.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:14.15,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Did he say some sweet things and sweep you off your feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:15.98,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you like to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:18.74,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I think I figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:22.70,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one person he truly loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:31.15,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Vito.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:34.84,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you'll have to excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:42.64,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid my lovely wife and I have plans for the rest of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:58.13,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like we're on a date, huh?
